<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Backerss — Academia · Ciclo 1</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Black&family=Archivo:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0B0B0A;
    --bg-raised: #141312;
    --bg-card: #171614;
    --ink: #F1EDE2;
    --ink-dim: #A39C8A;
    --ink-faint: #5C574A;
    --gold: #D4AF37;
    --gold-bright: #F0CC5B;
    --gold-dim: #4A3B14;
    --green: #3FA66A;
    --green-dim: #1E4A30;
    --line: #2A2722;
    --line-bright: #3D3829;
    --locked: #1C1B19;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 0px, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 3px);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  button { font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; }

  /* ---------- TOP BAR ---------- */
  .topbar {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 40;
    background: rgba(11,11,10,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .topbar-inner {
    max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .logo { font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif; font-size: 1.02rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--gold); }
  .logo .s { color: var(--ink); }

  .vault-chip {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-bright);
    background: var(--bg-raised);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .vault-chip .vc-icon { width: 14px; height: 14px; color: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .vault-chip .vc-label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.66rem; color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .vault-chip .vc-amount { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--gold-bright); font-weight: 600; margin-left: 2px; }

  /* ---------- MAIN ---------- */
  main { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 24px 100px; }

  .page-head { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .breadcrumb {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .breadcrumb .sep { color: var(--line-bright); margin: 0 8px; }
  .breadcrumb .here { color: var(--gold); }

  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.4vw, 2.1rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .page-sub { margin-top: 10px; color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 0.98rem; max-width: 520px; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ---------- CYCLE PROGRESS RAIL ---------- */
  .cycle-rail {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .rail-node {
    width: 9px; height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--line-bright);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .rail-node.done { background: var(--green); box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(63,166,106,0.5); }
  .rail-node.active { background: var(--gold); box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(212,175,55,0.6); }
  .rail-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--line-bright); }
  .rail-line.done { background: var(--green-dim); }

  /* ---------- ACTIVE MISSION CARD ---------- */
  .mission-card {
    margin-top: 36px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(212,175,55,0.06), transparent 55%), var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .mission-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold), var(--green));
  }

  .mission-head {
    padding: 28px 30px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .mission-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .mission-tag::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--gold);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.3; } }

  .mission-days {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .mission-body { padding: 14px 30px 30px; }
  .mission-title {
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    margin-top: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .mission-desc { margin-top: 12px; color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.65; max-width: 480px; }

  .mission-video-link {
    margin-top: 22px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-bright);
    background: transparent;
    padding: 13px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .mission-video-link:hover { border-color: var(--gold); background: rgba(212,175,55,0.06); }
  .mvl-icon {
    width: 30px; height: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .mvl-icon svg { width: 11px; height: 11px; margin-left: 1px; }
  .mvl-text { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .mvl-sub { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--ink-faint); margin-top: 1px; }

  /* ---------- GOAL STRIP ---------- */
  .goal-strip {
    margin-top: 26px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .goal-cell { background: var(--bg-raised); padding: 18px 20px; }
  .goal-num { font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--gold-bright); }
  .goal-label { margin-top: 4px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }

  /* ---------- CHECKLIST ---------- */
  .checklist { margin-top: 28px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .checklist-head {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 18px 0 14px;
  }
  .checklist-title { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .checklist-count { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--gold); }

  .check-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--line);
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .check-item:first-of-type { border-top: none; }

  .check-box {
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--line-bright);
    border-radius: 3px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.18s ease;
  }
  .check-item.checked .check-box {
    background: var(--gold);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }
  .check-box svg {
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.5);
    transition: all 0.18s ease;
    color: #0B0B0A;
  }
  .check-item.checked .check-box svg { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }

  .check-text { flex: 1; }
  .check-label { font-size: 0.94rem; color: var(--ink); transition: color 0.18s ease; }
  .check-item.checked .check-label { color: var(--ink-faint); text-decoration: line-through; text-decoration-color: var(--line-bright); }
  .check-meta { margin-top: 3px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--ink-faint); }

  /* ---------- CONSTELACIÓN (open-ended Backers registry) ---------- */
  .constellation {
    margin-top: 28px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top: 20px;
  }
  .constellation-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .constellation-title {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .constellation-count {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--green);
  }
  .constellation-sub {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .constellation-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 56px;
  }

  .backer-node {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    animation: node-appear 0.4s ease;
  }
  @keyframes node-appear {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  }
  .backer-node .dot {
    width: 18px; height: 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(63,166,106,0.7), 0 0 2px rgba(63,166,106,1);
  }
  .backer-node .tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .add-backer-btn {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--line-bright);
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .add-backer-btn:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }
  .add-backer-btn svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

  /* ---------- COMPLETE BUTTON ---------- */
  .mission-complete {
    margin-top: 30px;
    padding-top: 26px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .mc-note { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--ink-faint); max-width: 320px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .btn-complete {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--line-bright);
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 14px 26px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: none;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .btn-complete.is-ready {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #0B0B0A;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn-complete.is-ready:hover { box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(212,175,55,0.25); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-complete svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

  /* ---------- LOCKED MISSIONS (queue) ---------- */
  .queue-label {
    margin-top: 56px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .queue-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--line); }

  .locked-card {
    margin-top: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--locked);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 22px 26px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .locked-card + .locked-card { margin-top: 12px; }

  .locked-icon {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-bright);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .locked-icon svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; color: var(--ink-faint); }

  .locked-text .lt-title { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .locked-text .lt-sub { margin-top: 3px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--line-bright); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }

  /* ---------- VAULT FOOTER NOTE ---------- */
  .vault-note {
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding: 22px 26px;
    border: 1px solid var(--green-dim);
    background: rgba(63,166,106,0.05);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .vault-note-icon {
    width: 34px; height: 34px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .vault-note-icon svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; color: #0B0B0A; }
  .vault-note-text { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.55; }
  .vault-note-text strong { color: var(--green); }

  /* ---------- VIDEO MODAL ---------- */
  .video-modal-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(5,5,4,0.86);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    z-index: 200;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
  }
  .video-modal-overlay.is-open {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  .video-modal {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transform: scale(0.96) translateY(10px);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 100px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
  }
  .video-modal-overlay.is-open .video-modal {
    transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
  }

  .video-modal-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .vm-title {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .vm-title::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--gold);
  }
  .vm-close {
    width: 30px; height: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-bright);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .vm-close:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
  .vm-close svg { width: 13px; height: 13px; }

  .video-modal-body {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    background: #000;
  }
  .video-modal-body iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  /* Placeholder shown until a real video URL is connected */
  .vm-placeholder {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 40%, rgba(212,175,55,0.08), transparent), var(--bg-raised);
  }
  .vm-play {
    width: 64px; height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .vm-play svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; margin-left: 2px; }
  .vm-ph-label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.74rem; color: var(--ink-dim); }
  .vm-ph-label .dur { color: var(--gold); }

  .video-modal-foot {
    padding: 16px 22px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .video-modal { max-width: 100%; }
  }

  /* ---------- TOAST ---------- */
  .toast {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 28px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #0B0B0A;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 14px 26px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: all 0.35s ease;
    z-index: 100;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .toast.is-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    main { padding: 32px 18px 80px; }
    .mission-head { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .mission-title { font-size: 1.3rem; }
    .goal-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .mission-complete { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .btn-complete { justify-content: center; }
    .vault-chip .vc-label { display: none; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .mission-tag::before { animation: none !important; }
  }

  :focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--gold); outline-offset: 3px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-inner">
    <div class="logo">BACKER<span class="s">SS</span></div>
    <div class="vault-chip">
      <svg class="vc-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="10" rx="1"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
      <span class="vc-label">Bóveda</span>
      <span class="vc-amount mono" id="vaultAmount">$0</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<main>
  <div class="page-head">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      ACADEMIA <span class="sep">/</span> <span class="here">CICLO 1 · ACCIÓN DIRECTA</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="page-title">Bienvenido a tu Ciclo 1.</h1>
    <p class="page-sub">3 misiones. 90 días como techo máximo, sin piso mínimo. El volumen es tu única llave de paso — entre más rápido ejecutes, más rápido avanzas.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="cycle-rail" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="rail-node active"></div>
    <div class="rail-line"></div>
    <div class="rail-node"></div>
    <div class="rail-line"></div>
    <div class="rail-node"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ACTIVE MISSION -->
  <div class="mission-card">
    <div class="mission-head">
      <div class="mission-tag">Misión activa · Reto 1</div>
      <div class="mission-days mono">Días 1–3 · techo máximo</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mission-body">
      <h2 class="mission-title">El Baño de Realidad</h2>
      <p class="mission-desc">Tu meta mínima: 20 contactos reales desde tu página de captura. No estás cazando un "no" — estás cazando el contacto número 20. Si tu esfuerzo te da un "sí" antes de llegar, sigue contactando igual: el piso no cambia.</p>

      <button type="button" class="mission-video-link" id="openVideoModal">
        <span class="mvl-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#0B0B0A"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg></span>
        <span>
          <span class="mvl-text">Ver Video Briefing — Misión 1</span><br>
          <span class="mvl-sub">60 SEG · CONTEXTO, OBJETIVO Y POR QUÉ</span>
        </span>
      </button>

      <div class="goal-strip">
        <div class="goal-cell">
          <div class="goal-num mono" id="contactCount">0 / 20</div>
          <div class="goal-label">Contactos reales · mínimo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="goal-cell">
          <div class="goal-num mono" id="dayCount">Día 1</div>
          <div class="goal-label">De 3 (techo máximo)</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="checklist">
        <div class="checklist-head">
          <span class="checklist-title">Registro de campo</span>
          <span class="checklist-count" id="checklistCount">0 / 4</span>
        </div>

        <div class="check-item" data-value="7">
